data.description: Located in the highly desired Waterstone community on Lake Conroe this beautiful one story house has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms. The layout of the home is a open concept and connects the living room, breakfast area & kitchen creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings.Stainless steel appliances.Kitchen features latest designer colors and the kitchen also features spacious counter tops. Tile flooring and carpet; nearly 1/2 acre large backyard entirely fenced. The backyard is set up for plenty of room for entertaining, pets and the children can feel free to pla!. This house is conveniently located near schools and shopping centers Home is priced well and practically lived in!
